{"tid":814393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞女乘客與的士司機爭執  重慶大廈撲出近百人南亞漢包圍司機","createTime":"2018-09-11T08:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T09:24:42.000Z","uid":141060,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4abee87ebca39107d9a9e2abed316889690d3a86","tid":814393,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180911/58668340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F58668340&d=tYIKVQDHuTuwEEk%2FJ6p%2FTGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=920944c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F58668340&h=2e0369c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180911/58668340</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/161026_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F161026_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=1b57cb64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名的士司機，昨晚載着醉酒女乘客到尖沙嘴彌敦道重慶大廈，被對方指偷去她遺在車廂的手機。雙方起爭執互相拉扯，一度滾在地上「碌地沙」。重慶大廈附近的南亞漢，以為女同鄉被欺侮，撲出包圍的士司機，一時間群情洶湧。<br />\n讀者陳先生當時途經現場，目擊女乘客和司機爭執拉扯，雙雙倒地，要車上的男乘客落車將他們分開。當時近百人圍觀，當中數十人包圍住的士。而的士司機的T裇已經被扯爛露出左肩，氣氛緊張。幸警員迅速趕到，手持盾牌控制場面。陳先生聽到的士司機向警員說：「話我偷電話呀！」<br />\n警方回覆查詢稱，昨晚8時左右，南亞裔女乘客在深水埗乘的士到重慶大廈，到埗後落車，但隨即發現不見了手機，懷疑遺留在的士上，折返找尋，但沒有發現，因而與姓倪(56歲)司機起爭執。據悉，女乘客滿身酒氣，加上語言不通，雙方無法溝通，經警員調查，司機頸紅拒絕送院，並不追究，事件中無人被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e42fc4b69bcba8a540a376dab05377f8a5a18c","tid":814393,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:13:41.000Z",